## Proposed Changes

### Komponen 1: Backend — `ExpoPushService` Refactor

#### [MODIFY] [ExpoPushService.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/SIdispen%20(SMA%203)/backend-api/app/Services/ExpoPushService.php)

Refaktor method `send()` menjadi:

```php
public static function send($to, $title, $body, $data = [], $logForUserIds = [])
```

**Perubahan:**
1. **Batch-safe:** Jika `$to` berupa array token, buat array of message payloads (satu per token) sesuai Expo API best practice.
2. **Auto-log:** Parameter `$logForUserIds` (array user ID) → simpan record ke tabel `notifications` untuk tiap user. Kolom yang diisi: `user_id`, `title`, `body`, `tipe` (dari `$data['type']`), `reference_id` (dari `$data['ticket_id']`).
3. **Silent fail:** Tetap gunakan try-catch + `Log::error` agar proses utama (create tiket, approve, dll) tidak terganggu.

