### Komponen 3: Backend — NotificationController Endpoints Baru

#### [MODIFY] [NotificationController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/SIdispen%20(SMA%203)/backend-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/NotificationController.php)

Tambahkan 2 method baru:

```php
// POST /notifications/mark-all-read
public function markAllRead(Request $request)
{
    Notification::where('user_id', $request->user()->id)
        ->where('is_read', false)
        ->update(['is_read' => true]);
    return response()->json(['message' => 'All marked as read']);
}

// GET /notifications/unread-count
public function unreadCount(Request $request)
{
    $count = Notification::where('user_id', $request->user()->id)
        ->where('is_read', false)
        ->count();
    return response()->json(['count' => $count]);
}
```

