### Komponen 6: Mobile — Push Notification Hook

#### [NEW] `mobile-app/src/hooks/usePushNotifications.ts`

Hook ini menangani seluruh lifecycle push notification:

```typescript
// 1. Setup notification handler (foreground behavior)
Notifications.setNotificationHandler({
  handleNotification: async () => ({
    shouldShowAlert: true,
    shouldPlaySound: true,
    shouldSetBadge: false,
  }),
});

export const usePushNotifications = () => {
  // State: expoPushToken, notification
  
  useEffect(() => {
    // A. Request permission & generate token
    registerForPushNotificationsAsync().then(token => {
      if (token) {
        setExpoPushToken(token);
        // Kirim ke backend POST /user/device-token
        api.post('/user/device-token', { device_token: token }).catch(console.error);
      }
    });

    // B. Foreground listener
    notificationListener.current = Notifications.addNotificationReceivedListener(...);

    // C. Response listener (deep link saat notif ditekan)
    responseListener.current = Notifications.addNotificationResponseReceivedListener(response => {
      const data = response.notification.request.content.data;
      if (data?.ticket_id) {
        router.push(`/ticket/${data.ticket_id}`);
      }
    });

    return () => { /* cleanup subscriptions */ };
  }, []);

  return { expoPushToken, notification };
};
```

**Fungsi `registerForPushNotificationsAsync()`:**
1. Setup Android channel (`default`, importance MAX, vibration, `lightColor: '#1B5E20'`)
2. Check `Device.isDevice` (harus physical device)
3. Request permissions
4. Get `projectId` dari `Constants.expoConfig.extra.eas.projectId`
5. Return `Notifications.getExpoPushTokenAsync({ projectId }).data`

