### Komponen 8: Mobile — Notifications Screen (Real Data)

#### [MODIFY] [notifications.tsx](file:///c:/laragon/www/SIdispen%20(SMA%203)/mobile-app/app/notifications.tsx)

Ganti seluruh data dummy dengan integrasi API real:

1. **Fetch:** `GET /notifications` → map response ke format `NotificationBanner`
2. **Mark as read:** Saat item di-tap → `PUT /notifications/{id}/read`
3. **Mark all read:** Tombol "Baca Semua" → `POST /notifications/mark-all-read`
4. **Deep link:** Saat item di-tap → route ke `/ticket/[reference_id]` berdasarkan field `tipe` dan `reference_id`
5. **Pull-to-refresh:** `FlatList` dengan `onRefresh` + `refreshing` state
6. **Type mapping:** Map `tipe` dari DB ke `NotificationBanner` type prop:
   - `new_ticket`, `ticket_forwarded` → `warning`
   - `ticket_approved`, `qr_validated` → `success`
   - `ticket_rejected` → `error`
   - `chat` → `info`

