### Komponen 9: Mobile — Supabase Realtime Chat

#### [MODIFY] [chat/[id].tsx](file:///c:/laragon/www/SIdispen%20(SMA%203)/mobile-app/app/chat/[id].tsx)

Tambahkan Supabase Realtime subscription:

```typescript
import { supabase } from '../../src/utils/supabaseClient';

useEffect(() => {
  const channel = supabase
    .channel(`chat_${ticketId}`)
    .on(
      'postgres_changes',
      {
        event: 'INSERT',
        schema: 'public',
        table: 'ticket_chats',
        filter: `dispensasi_ticket_id=eq.${ticketId}`,
      },
      (payload) => {
        // Append pesan baru ke state tanpa refresh
        setMessages(prev => [payload.new, ...prev]);
      }
    )
    .subscribe();

  return () => { supabase.removeChannel(channel); };
}, [ticketId]);
```

> [!NOTE]
> **Prasyarat Supabase:** Pastikan Replication untuk tabel `ticket_chats` sudah diaktifkan di Dashboard Supabase → Database → Replication. Tanpa ini, event `postgres_changes` tidak akan dipancarkan.

